Ok you know the jaz...

Nuke the Page

This bookmarklet will enable you to play a game to nuke the page! Use the arrow keys to move, and space to shoot.

Script: javascript:var KICKASSVERSION='2.0';var s = document.createElement('script');s.type='text/javascript';document.body.appendChild(s);s.src='//hi.kickassapp.com/kickass.js';void(0);
---
Fontbomb

This bookmarklet gives you the power to place exploding bombs on a page. This will give the words a cool effect of movement around the explosion.

Script: javascript:(function () {var s = document.createElement('script');s.setAttribute('src', 'http://fontbomb.ilex.ca/js/main.js');document.body.appendChild(s);}());
---
Katamari

Personally my favorite bookmarklet, this gives you a ball to roll around and pack up the words and elements on a page to the ball, allowing it to grow bigger. It's really fun to use.

